Why not just replace the bellhousing?

>P.S. What years trannys will work in this application?

72-75 will bolt up, but of those only 72-73 have the same ratios.  Make 
sure it says "002" on the side and not "091" and that it has the bolt holes 
in the top of the bellhousing where it hangs from the chassis.

